<view class="page-shell login-page">
  <view class="hero-card panel">
    <view class="hero-glow hero-glow-left"></view>
    <view class="hero-glow hero-glow-right"></view>

    <text class="hero-kicker">YUCSSA CAMPUS HUB</text>
    <text class="hero-title">把学生会小程序重新做成真正能服务校园生活的入口。</text>
    <text class="hero-copy">
      不再只是一个静态商家目录，而是把活动、福利、服务和会员身份放进同一套体验里。
    </text>

    <view class="hero-badges">
      <view class="hero-badge">学生优惠</view>
      <view class="hero-badge">活动更新</view>
      <view class="hero-badge">成员服务</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="story-list">
    <block wx:for="{{onboardingHighlights}}" wx:key="*this">
      <view class="story-card panel">
        <text class="story-index">0{{index + 1}}</text>
        <text class="story-copy">{{item}}</text>
      </view>
    </block>
  </view>

  <view class="action-card panel">
    <text class="action-title">先进入体验，再决定接不接后端。</text>
    <text class="action-copy">
      当前版本全部基于本地 mock 数据，可直接在微信开发者工具中演示完整流程。
    </text>

    <button class="primary-button" bindtap="handleQuickStart">立即进入体验版</button>

    <button
      wx:if="{{canUseProfile}}"
      class="secondary-button"
      bindtap="handleProfileLogin"
    >
      使用微信头像昵称
    </button>
  </view>
</view>
